<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((التعليق الرغيب)</span>) <span class="c2">(٣/ ١٢٥)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الشَّيْخُ:</span> الرِّوَايَةُ كُلُّهَا: <span class="c2">((زَوْر)</span>)،<span class="c5"> وَالصَّوَابُ:</span> <span class="c2">((زُور)</span>): أَنْ تُضَمَّ الزَّايُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>